  "datePublished": "2026-03-09",
  "description": "A hard hand in [blackjack](../index.md) is a hand whose total does not include an ace counted as 11 [@thorp1966]. Either the hand has no ace at all, or any ace it contains must count as 1 to avoid a [bust](./bust.md). A 10-6 is a hard 16. Ace-6-10 is also a hard 17, because the ace can no longer remain 11.",
  "name": "hard hand",
